    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>
                        <persName><name>Gospertus</name></persName> mulinario, avitator infra <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs> ista <placeName key="#Cities"
                            >Lucense</placeName> prope <geogName ref="#estates/3304"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention">curte domne regine</geogName>,
                        filius <persName>quondam <name>Lazari</name></persName> viene posto da
                            <persName ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops">Hieremias</persName> gratia
                        Dei <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs> (…) livellario ordine (…) in casa
                        illa, in qua ego ipsi abitare videor prope suprascripta <geogName
                            ref="#estates/3304" key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention">curte domne
                            regine</geogName>, pertinentes <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1705" key="#Churches">Sancti Petri que
                            dicitur ad Vincula, et Sancti Geminiani</orgName>; iam dicta casa cum
                        orto, sive riparia et sepe mulinaria, ubi ego ipsi modo molino, avere visu
                        sum, (…). Obbligo di in ipsa casa residere et abitare (…); et tam ipsa casa
                        quam et orto (…) bene excolere et gubernare seo meliorare (…). Censo (pro
                        iustitia): per singulos annos in festivitate suprascripte ecclesie Sancti
                        Geminiani in suprascripta ecclesia ad presbiteroillo qui pro tempore in ipsa
                        ecclesia ordinatus fuerit, census reddere debeamus argentum denarios bonos
                        expendiviles numero tres tantum; et pro suprascripta riparia, dum predicto
                        molino inibi abuerimus (…) ad parte prefate ecclesie Sancit Geminiani vel
                        suis rectoribus, per singulos annos per omnem ebdomadas, uno sistario de
                        grano mundo ad legitimo sistario mensurato; et a mandato vestro venire (…)
                        legem et iustitiam faciendum (…). Pena: argentum solidos quinquaginta (…).
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus"
                            >Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/1558 #places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalpertus</name></persName> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Baldipertus">Baldiperti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Hildiprandus</name></persName> flio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Ildefredus">Hiltifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> filio
                                <persName><name ref="Philippus/de Suborbano">Filippi</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/487">Suborbano</placeName></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Teofridus"
                            >Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabinus</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
